{"type":"message","id":"2f5da8e2","parentId":"4e92fa7c","timestamp":"2026-03-11T23:49:46.634Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"functions.memory_get:0","toolName":"memory_get","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"text\": \"# MEMORY.md — Curated Long-Term Memory\\n\\n> **Purpose:** Distilled wisdom, patterns, preferences, and operational notes.\\n> **Security:** **ONLY loaded in main session** (direct chats with Matt). Never in shared contexts.\\n> **Last Updated:** 2026-02-18\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Reference Files — Quick Navigation\\n\\n| File | Purpose | Last Updated |\\n|------|---------|--------------|\\n| **WHOAMI.md** | Persona, roles, responsibilities, skills inventory | 2026-02-18 |\\n| **UNDERSTANDING-PRD.md** | Architecture guide, CRM system, operational patterns | 2026-02-18 |\\n| **PRD.md** | Canonical feature inventory (source of truth) | 2026-02-17 |\\n| **AGENTS.md** | Rules of engagement, task execution, safety | (see file) |\\n| **SOUL.md** | Personality, communication style | (see file) |\\n\\n---\\n\\n## User Profile Reference\\n\\n- **Name:** Matt\\n- **Timezone:** Asia/Singapore (GMT+8) / PST when working\\n- **Work pattern:** Early bird (~7am)\\n- **Email:** Three accounts (personal, YouTube, work)\\n- **Primary channel:** Telegram (various topics)\\n- **WhatsApp:** +6591127357\\n- **Core projects:** Content creation, AI/tech focus, YouTube channel\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Operational Patterns\\n\\n### Daily Ping (7 AM Asia/Singapore)\\n**Cron job:** `daily-ping-telegram` | **Status:** Enabled | **Timeout:** 15 minutes\\n\\n**Data Sources:**\\n- Bitcoin: CoinGecko API (price + 24h change)\\n- Stocks: yfinance (NVDA, MSFT, GOOGL, INTC, META, AMD with delta)\\n- GitHub: Trending repos (top 10, created recently with high star velocity)\\n- Delivery: Telegram (ID: 1087368827)\\n\\n**Format:**\\n```\\n📈 Crypto\\n• Bitcoin: $PRICE (📈/📉 CHANGE%)\\n\\n💹 Tech Stocks\\n• SYMBOL $PRICE (📈/📉 CHANGE%)\",\n  \"path\": \"MEMORY.md\"\n}"}],"details":{"text":"# MEMORY.md — Curated Long-Term Memory\n\n> **Purpose:** Distilled wisdom, patterns, preferences, and operational notes.\n> **Security:** **ONLY loaded in main session** (direct chats with Matt). Never in shared contexts.\n> **Last Updated:** 2026-02-18\n\n---\n\n## Reference Files — Quick Navigation\n\n| File | Purpose | Last Updated |\n|------|---------|--------------|\n| **WHOAMI.md** | Persona, roles, responsibilities, skills inventory | 2026-02-18 |\n| **UNDERSTANDING-PRD.md** | Architecture guide, CRM system, operational patterns | 2026-02-18 |\n| **PRD.md** | Canonical feature inventory (source of truth) | 2026-02-17 |\n| **AGENTS.md** | Rules of engagement, task execution, safety | (see file) |\n| **SOUL.md** | Personality, communication style | (see file) |\n\n---\n\n## User Profile Reference\n\n- **Name:** Matt\n- **Timezone:** Asia/Singapore (GMT+8) / PST when working\n- **Work pattern:** Early bird (~7am)\n- **Email:** Three accounts (personal, YouTube, work)\n- **Primary channel:** Telegram (various topics)\n- **WhatsApp:** +6591127357\n- **Core projects:** Content creation, AI/tech focus, YouTube channel\n\n---\n\n## Operational Patterns\n\n### Daily Ping (7 AM Asia/Singapore)\n**Cron job:** `daily-ping-telegram` | **Status:** Enabled | **Timeout:** 15 minutes\n\n**Data Sources:**\n- Bitcoin: CoinGecko API (price + 24h change)\n- Stocks: yfinance (NVDA, MSFT, GOOGL, INTC, META, AMD with delta)\n- GitHub: Trending repos (top 10, created recently with high star velocity)\n- Delivery: Telegram (ID: 1087368827)\n\n**Format:**\n```\n📈 Crypto\n• Bitcoin: $PRICE (📈/📉 CHANGE%)\n\n💹 Tech Stocks\n• SYMBOL $PRICE (📈/📉 CHANGE%)","path":"MEMORY.md"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773272986628}}
