{"type":"message","id":"f639e534","parentId":"77621338","timestamp":"2026-03-12T15:52:59.278Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" The user sent a hello message. Their previous request was to read YAML headers of skills in `/home/pete/.claude/skills/` and create an inventory. I started this process but haven't completed it yet. I should acknowledge the hello and also let them know I'm in the process of building the skills inventory they asked for. I could also give a","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":" Hey! Still working through the skills inventory from your earlier request. I found **~100 skill directories** in `/home/pete/.claude/skills/` — now extracting YAML headers and categorizing them.\n\nQuick preview of what I'm seeing:\n\n**Development & Coding**\n- `nextjs-tailwind-v4-luxe`, `frontend-design`, `backend-development`\n- `mcp-builder`, `app-builder`, `code-review`\n- `nodejs-best-practices`, `python-patterns`, `clean-code`\n\n**Security & Quality**\n- `vulnerability-scanner`, `red-team-tactics`, `webapp-testing`\n- `lint-and-validate`, `tdd-workflow`, `testing-patterns`\n\n**Design & Content**\n- `aesthetic`, `canvas-design`, `algorithmic-art`\n- `artifacts-builder`, `brand-guidelines`, `ui-styling`\n\n**Infrastructure**\n- `deployment-procedures`, `server-management`, `databases`\n- `mcp-management`, `devops`, `bash-linux`\n\n**Automation & Business**\n- `connect-apps`, `file-organizer`, `lead-research-assistant`\n- `invoice-organizer`, `content-research-writer`\n\nShould I continue extracting all headers and create a comprehensive categorized inventory for MEMORY.md? It's a substantial list — good to have documented for future reference."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"moonshotai/kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp